Name: Product Segmentation Validation
SBQQ__ErrorMessage__c:
Product Configuration Error!
Products Must be segmented to print, send, or close this Quote.
Check for any Lines in the "Standard Products" section that have a Magic Wand Icon and click the Icon to Segment the Line.

Name: Set Account on Options for BB
Fix This Blue Book Without Account Sequence
SBQQ__ErrorMessage__c: Blue Book products must have an Account Sequence on the Quote Line.

Name: Proview Product Validation
SBQQ__ErrorMessage__c: The Proview Product must be added to the Quote when a Blue Book product is present.

Name: Print Product Without Address Validation
SBQQ__ErrorMessage__c: Print products must have a Shipping Address on the Quote Line.

Name: Is Missing BI Seats / AIACC Alert
SBQQ__ErrorMessage__c: Some Product(s) on this Quote Require BI Seats / AIACC. Please add it to the Quote.

Name: Segment Quantities Are Not Equal
SBQQ__ErrorMessage__c: The product quantity for each year does match.  Please check the quantities to ensure they are the same in every period.
